Please don't trust @tatamotorscars because my Tata Nexon suddenly catches fire while I'm brother is driving on the road. Don't be fooled by the 5-star safety rating; don't put yourself and your family at risk. Tata's investigation team has acknowledged the possibility of a sudden fire while driving in the car during all investigations. However, Tata Nexon, in an attempt to conceal their own shortcomings, even rejected our insurance claim, claiming it would expose them to their own accusations. The mistake was that we trusted both Tata Insurance Company and Tata Motors.
